{
  "text": "This is a point that I find quite confusing to me. It is a function of the free will of the positively polarized energy to move into negatively polarized time space. However, it is also a function of his lack of understanding of what he is doing. It is a function of his negatively polarized other self, creating a situation by which he is, shall I say, lured to that configuration? What is the principle with respect to the first distortion that allows this to occur since we have two portions of the creator, each of equal value, or equal potential, shall I say, but oppositely polarized. And we have this situation resulting. Could you tell me the philosophical principle behind this particular act? I am Ra. There are two important points in this regard. Free will does not mean that there will be no circumstances when calculations will be a right. Although there are no mistakes, there are surprises. Secondly, that which we and you do in workings such as this carries a magical charge if you would use this much misunderstood term, perhaps we may say a metaphysical power. Those who do a work of power are available for communication to and from entities of a roughly similar power. Each is a working in consciousness, but the group has not begun a work as a group.",
